# Profit Or Loss Unrealised Change In Creditworthiness Fair Value Gains Net Amount

## identifier
de7680

## type
float

## definition
This is the net value, as at the relevant date, of any unrealised fair value gains and (losses) arising from changes in the reporting party's creditworthiness.

## guidance
A gain may arise, for example, from a reduction in fair value of the reporting party's outstanding debt due to a change in credit rating.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.Unrealised.ChangeInCreditworthinessFairValueGainsNet.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=instant
